data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 3-level Cape Cod home, a true gem in the desirable Snowden Bridge community. This picturesque residence is a testament to classic charm and modern luxury, surrounded by beautifully landscaped grounds both in the front and back.  As you approach the front of the house, you'll be immediately drawn to the inviting front porch, a perfect spot to enjoy your morning coffee or watch the world go by. The lovely landscaping enhances the curb appeal, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere.  Step inside, and you'll find a main level that exudes elegance and functionality. The primary bedroom with an en-suite bathroom offers a serene retreat, while an additional bedroom and full bathroom provide versatility for guests or family members. Beautiful hardwood floors grace the formal living room, dining room, and family room, creating a seamless flow throughout the main level.  The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, a chef's dream with stainless steel appliances, a double wall oven, glass cooktop, and upgraded countertops. The large breakfast room bathed in natural light is the perfect setting for casual meals and family gatherings. The family room, with its cozy ambiance and gas fireplace, provides access to the back screened-in porch, where you can enjoy the outdoors in comfort, thanks to the ceiling fan. The backyard is a true oasis, featuring a large patio, perfect for al fresco dining and entertaining.  Venture to the upper level, and you'll discover a versatile bonus room that can be transformed into a home office, playroom, or media room. Two additional bedrooms and another full bathroom on this level offer ample space for family and guests.  The lower level of this home is an entertainer's dream, boasting a spacious rec room with a well-appointed full bar/wet bar area, ideal for hosting gatherings and celebrations. An additional full bath and potential 5th bedroom on this level provides flexibility for guests. Abundant finished and unfinished storage spaces ensure that you'll have room for all your belongings.  The Snowden Bridge community offers an array of amenities, including a pool, parks, walking trails, and more, providing endless opportunities for recreation and relaxation.  This stunning Cape Cod home is more than just a house; it's a sanctuary where memories are made and cherished. With its blend of classic style, modern amenities, and beautiful outdoor spaces, this property is the embodiment of the ideal family home. Don't miss your chance to make it yours and experience the joy of living here.   *NEW Appliances in the last 2 years, NEW garage door opener in 2023*
